channel.title: Getting XP with a new skill logs
channel.description: Hi, I posted something like this before, but fixed it and found out the REAL error. When ever I level up with my new skill"S", it logs the levelers out. I can level up with any other skill but my made. I redid on Pimpscape and it worked perfectly find. But I have my main server on Cheezscape 80. Someone please tell me how to fix it.[br][size=1]Posted on: January 30, 2007, 06:06:17 PM[/size][hr]Oh come on! I posted on 7 posts helping people in the last 5 minutes, and no one helped me :( lol[br][size=1]Posted on: January 30, 2007, 06:27:39 PM[/size][hr]Fine then... All can be that way and ruin my skill for everyone lol. I guess no one but me can use =\
